{
  "texts": [
    "Incorporation of such AI models into existing CASA systems could further reduce the need for sperm staining in the future, especially in the context of surgically retrieved or frozen sperm with unknown viability.",
    "To our knowledge, no computer-aided systems exist to improve the surgical retrieval of sperm yet.",
    "Current testicular sperm extraction techniques for ICSI can be challenging, with outcomes being greatly operator-dependent 59.",
    "However, AI techniques to aid identification of sperm from biopsies during testicular sperm extraction have been investigated.",
    "describe a deep CNN capable of finding sperm in testicular biopsy samples with good accuracy (mean average precision of 0.74) but did not compare this to standard embryology techniques 60."
  ]
}